### C. Security headers — DONE
Applied to `/(.*)` via `next.config.mjs` `headers()`:
- `Content-Security-Policy`: full policy with Stripe / Sentry / PostHog / Cal.com allowlists, `frame-ancestors 'none'`, `upgrade-insecure-requests`, `object-src 'none'`
