## Env vars Julian must set in Vercel to activate Sentry

| Var | Value source | Required? |
|-----|--------------|-----------|
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_SENTRY_DSN` | Sentry project → Settings → Client Keys (DSN) | Yes — without it Sentry is a no-op |
| `SENTRY_DSN` | Same DSN (or omit if you reuse `NEXT_PUBLIC_*`) | Optional |
| `SENTRY_ORG` | Sentry org slug | Required for source-map upload |
| `SENTRY_PROJECT` | Sentry project slug | Required for source-map upload |
| `SENTRY_AUTH_TOKEN` | Sentry → Settings → Auth Tokens (scope: project:releases) | Required for source-map upload |

Without `SENTRY_AUTH_TOKEN`, builds succeed silently and source maps just don't upload — no breakage.

